819
01:19:04.613 --> 01:19:06.078
O nee.

820
01:19:11.768 --> 01:19:15.034
Ga. Stefano.

821
01:19:26.225 --> 01:19:27.860
Help me.

822
01:19:29.681 --> 01:19:32.320
Help me.

823
01:19:40.124 --> 01:19:42.899
Schiet een touw voor me.
